description:
Danny is solo this week talking about The Hills reboot gossip and lots of Bravo! He breaks down the most recent episode of The Real Housewives of Dallas where the girls get loose beer-bonging at a country western bar, and The Real Housewives of Orange County where there were Eddie headshots and death threats.

The Bravo/#RHOD talk starts at 15:00

#RHOC Recap starts at 34:50
